Radio News Reader
=================================

Connects to multiple mp3 radio streams using Akka actors, and displays text of audio transcripts using Google Speech Recognition API.

Uses Play Framework 2.3

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `activator dist`.

Try adding the following stations as an example:

BBC News [http://bbcwssc.ic.llnwd.net/stream/bbcwssc_mp1_ws-eieuk]
KQED [http://streams2.kqed.org:80/kqedradio]